description:
Arnott's Vita Weat Original has a source of fibre, 100% natural and plant based. Made from 100% wholegrains. For digestive well-being.

A deliciously healthy way to lunch...

Arnott's Vita-Weat are made from 100% wholegrains. They are a natural source of fibre to help support your digestive wellbeing and a source of Vitamin B3 to help unlock energy.

The perfect partner to your favourite healthy toppings, our delicious, plant-based crispbreads are a convenient, crunchy way to lunch!

For more lunch inspiration visit us at www.arnotts.com

Aussie made & loved

Four crispbreads = 40% of your daily wholegrains (based on the recommended 48g Wholegrain Daily Target Intake for adults).

Open up to positive eating.
name: Arnott's Vita Weat Crispbread Original 250G
